It's [FRENCH].

00:44:58.460 --> 00:44:58.960
It is.

00:44:58.960 --> 00:45:01.630
Because we believe
that because we

00:45:01.630 --> 00:45:04.750
come from such an
intellectual background, yes?

00:45:04.750 --> 00:45:09.100
We believe that if we
mark our opposition,

00:45:09.100 --> 00:45:11.939
it shows that we have
thought about it.

00:45:11.939 --> 00:45:12.730
That we're smarter.

00:45:12.730 --> 00:45:14.650
So culture is huge.

